pullrequest.title: Add a new semi-supervised test case

content.raw:
I made some changes and @ericr86 this is ready for you to review now. 

Currently the semisupervised test case use the simpleseg test case, and add supervision label on regions where simpleseg will mistakenly classified two clusters into 1.
